  ('dietitian-moex-02536', 'dietitian', 'dietitian-moex-105-cd594556', 'sub-dietitian-03', NULL, 'single_choice', '下列有關身體組成測量方法的敘述，何者正確？', '["以水中測量體重的方法評估身體組成時，可得到體表面積", "利用生物電阻（bioelectrical impedance）評估身體組成時，電阻越小表示脂肪越多", "以全身電導度法（TOBEC）評估身體組成時，可測得全身瘦體組織的量", "以雙能X光吸收法（DEXA）評估身體組成時，會暴露於輻射線"]'::jsonb, 3, NULL, TRUE, 'official', TRUE, 1, '{"parser_version": "moex_license_v1.0", "parsed_at": "2026-04-25T04:30:59+00:00", "source_pdf_sha1": "5bce608a3eb5", "answer_pdf_sha1": "a43367a2784c", "source_family": "moex-gov-tw", "moex": {"exam_code": "105030", "c": "103", "s": "0202", "q": "1"}, "raw_section_label": "乙、測驗題部分", "subject": "營養學", "year": "105", "exam_name": "105年第一次中醫師分階段、營養師心理師護理師社工師考試", "original_question_number": 16, "answer_corrected": false, "flags": [], "slug": "dietitian", "db_exam_id": "dietitian"}'::jsonb, NULL),
